<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="116" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,330,573]" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,538,366,393]" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Report associated with sponges:</emphasis>
This species was mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation author="Crowell, R. M." box="[911,1085,367,393]" pageId="15" pageNumber="116" pagination="265 - 270" refId="ref15456" refString="Crowell, R. M. (1990) Unionicola billieaehonore, new species, a sponge-associated Hydracarina (Acari: Unionicolidae) from New Zealand. New Zealand Journal of Zoology, 17 (2), 265 - 270. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 03014223.1990.10422601" type="journal article" year="1990">Crowell (1990)</bibRefCitation>
as developmentally associated with freshwater sponges in the Northern Hemisphere.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,330,573]" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,269,439,465]" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Remarks:</emphasis>
This species was reported from Ibi River, Ishizu, Kaizu, 
<collectingRegion box="[935,986,439,465]" country="Japan" name="Gifu" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Gifu</collectingRegion>
<collectingCountry box="[996,1060,439,465]" name="Japan" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Japan</collectingCountry>
(Imamura 1953) and 
<collectingRegion box="[1314,1432,439,465]" country="Iran" name="Kordestan" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Kordestan</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[198,456,475,501]" country="Iran" name="Kermanshah" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Kermanshah Province</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[475,520,475,501]" name="Iran" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hevers, J." box="[543,698,475,501]" pageId="15" pageNumber="116" pagination="265 - 280" refId="ref16786" refString="Hevers, J. (1984) Die Unionicola crassipes-Gruppe in Japan und in Iran. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift, 31 (4 - 5), 265 - 280." type="journal article" year="1984">Hevers 1984</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Viets, K. H. &amp; Plate, H." box="[725,979,474,501]" pageId="15" pageNumber="116" pagination="459 - 494" refId="ref20900" refString="Viets, K. H. &amp; Plate, H. (1954) Die Oekologischen (Parasitologischen) Beziehungen zwischen Wassermilben (Hydrachnellae, Acari) und Susswasser-Mollusken. Zeitschrift fur angewandte Entomologie, 35, 459 - 494. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1439 - 0418.1954. tb 00736. x" type="journal article" year="1954">Viets &amp; Plate (1954)</bibRefCitation>
reported it from a mussel, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lamarck" authorityYear="1799" box="[1327,1436,475,501]" class="Bivalvia" family="Unionidae" genus="Anodonta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Unionida" pageId="15" pageNumber="116" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1327,1436,475,501]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Anodonta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(= 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Starobogatov in Zatravkin" authorityYear="1983" box="[223,349,511,536]" class="Bivalvia" family="Unionidae" genus="Beringiana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Unionida" pageId="15" pageNumber="116" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[223,349,511,536]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">Beringiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) 
<emphasis box="[368,491,511,537]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="116">beringiana</emphasis>
Middendorff. It needs further study (emphasizing on developmental study) of this mite to get a better idea about it association with freshwater sponges.
</paragraph>
